snippet.title: Cobi Treasure Deluxe
snippet.description:
Help Sally the Seahorse collect and match all the ocean treasure as it falls to the Seabed.
 
Match the falling ocean gems and play through 3 exciting and absorbing game modes in this perfect blend of relaxation and gem matching fun for all the family.

Available on PC.
